---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

---

<Layout title="About Omega Detailing | Our Passion & Mission">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="bg-white pt-36 md:pt-72 pb-24 text-neutral-900 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="mb-16 animate-fade-in">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-tight">
          ABOUT <span class="text-blue-600">OMEGA</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-blue-600 mb-12"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-neutral-600">
          <p>
            Omega Detailing is a premium South African automotive detailing company dedicated to delivering exceptional vehicle care, preservation, and restoration. Driven by a passion for automotive excellence, we provide professional mobile detailing services that bring showroom-quality results directly to your doorstep.
          </p>
          <p>
            We understand that a vehicle is more than just transportation—it's an investment, a reflection of its owner, and something worth protecting. Our services are designed to restore, enhance, and preserve every aspect of your vehicle, from deep interior cleaning and paint decontamination to paint correction, ceramic coatings, and long-term surface protection.
          </p>
          <p>
            Using industry-leading products, advanced techniques, and meticulous attention to detail, we work to improve gloss, clarity, cleanliness, and overall condition while helping to protect your vehicle from everyday wear and environmental damage.
          </p>
          <p>
            As a fully mobile detailing service, Omega Detailing combines convenience with uncompromising quality, delivering professional results wherever your vehicle is located. Whether your car requires routine maintenance, paint enhancement, or comprehensive restoration, we are committed to exceeding expectations and achieving the highest standard of finish.
          </p>
          
          <div class="pt-8 text-center md:text-left">
            <a href="/pricing" class="inline-block px-10 py-5 bg-blue-600 text-white font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-neutral-900 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-blue-600/10">
              Explore Our Services
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 border-2 border-blue-600/20 group-hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-500"></div>
          <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 p-12 aspect-square flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-6">
             <div class="text-blue-600">
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-16 h-16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                 <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z" />
               </svg>
             </div>
             <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-900">James Bell</h3>
             <p class="text-[10px] text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-black">Founder & Lead Detailer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Generalized & Simple-But-Professional Detailing Guide Section */}
    <div class="mt-40 pt-40 border-t border-neutral-100 pb-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mb-24">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-tight">
          THE ART OF <br/>
          <span class="text-blue-600 italic">CAR DETAILING.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-2xl text-neutral-600 font-light leading-relaxed italic">
          Detailing is the refined elevation of a vehicle’s condition. It is a systematic process of restoration and preservation that returns a luxury car to its most pristine state through meticulous attention to every square inch.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        {/* Exterior Generalization */}
        <div class="bg-neutral-50 p-10 border border-neutral-200 space-y-6">
           <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[.4em] text-blue-600">Restoration</h3>
           <p class="font-bold text-xl uppercase tracking-tighter">Surface Elevation</p>
           <p class="text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
             Beyond mere washing, detailing focuses on the microscopic restoration of exterior surfaces. By refining the finish and eliminating the signs of environmental wear, we restore a depth of clarity and brilliance that defines a showroom masterpiece.
           </p>
        </div>

        {/* Interior Generalization */}
        <div class="bg-neutral-50 p-10 border border-neutral-200 space-y-6">
           <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[.4em] text-blue-600">Metamorphosis</h3>
           <p class="font-bold text-xl uppercase tracking-tighter">Internal Refinement</p>
           <p class="text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
             The interior is treated with a level of care that transcends cleaning. It is a total rejuvenation of the cabin’s environment—refreshing every surface, texture, and element to recapture the factory-fresh aura and tactile perfection of a high-end vehicle.
           </p>
        </div>

        {/* Purpose Generalization */}
        <div class="bg-neutral-50 p-10 border border-neutral-200 space-y-6">
           <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[.4em] text-blue-600">Preservation</h3>
           <p class="font-bold text-xl uppercase tracking-tighter">Integrity of Value</p>
           <p class="text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
             Detailing is the definitive method of long-term preservation. By maintaining the aesthetic and structural integrity of a vehicle, you safeguard its status as an elite asset while ensuring it continues to deliver a premium experience year after year.
           </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mt-24 space-y-12 text-neutral-600 text-lg leading-relaxed font-light">
         <h4 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-neutral-900 italic">An Essential Standard for Quality</h4>
         <p>
           Detailing is an essential standard for keeping your vehicle in peak condition. Regular care protects against environmental wear and tear, ensuring that it looks and feels like new for every journey.
         </p>
         <p>
           At Omega Detailing, we approach every job with meticulous care and dedication. Our mobile service is designed to maintain your vehicle’s value, appearance, and overall appeal over the long term.
         </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
  }
  main { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
</style>
